headline: 3 Reasons Vici Properties Is a Must-Buy for Long-Term Investors
summary: Vici Properties is a real estate investment trust (REIT) that benefits from the popularity of gambling.  Here are three reasons why long-term investors will want to take a close look at buying Vici Properties.  The most important thing to understand about Vici is that it is not a casino operator.
